Organisms
    -Composed of molecules and atoms
    -higher level abstraction
    -may be a 'facade' pattern
        -hides complexity

Tip 1: Strong Opinions are  Feature
    -What underlying props should be exposed from underlying props?
    -Enforce Consistency
    -smaller API
    -easier to understand
    -single, clear purpose
    -less surface area to test
    -less complexity, less code, less bugs

Tip 2: Keep your Organisms Dumb
    -Organisms != App
    -Use containers to save people time
    